HEADWORD: Buoyage
<hw>Buoy"age</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>Buoys, taken
collectively; a series of buoys, as for the guidance of vessels into or
out of port; the providing of buoys.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

